had to try.  She jumped up and down and waved her arms.*

"Hey, Anyone in there?" she yelled.

*She felt like an idiot.  She knew they wouldn't take her into the group and 
let her live.  Was she suicidal?  No, she didn't think so.  But what in her

but still knew that this was something that she HAD to do.*
